          <p class='first-para'>
            I thank the Minister for her response. Presumably, this would affect new water suppliers too&#x2014;they would fall within this restriction.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0647P0-02372'>
        <a name='S5LV0647P0_20030410_GCR_35'>  </a>
