      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0647P0-02400'>
        <a name='S5LV0647P0_20030410_GCR_63'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0647P0_20030410_GCR_63' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Whitty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-whitty" title="Mr John Whitty">Lord Whitty</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I cannot even find the right page on Amendment No. 168M, so I will have to dig beyond my initial explanation and write to the noble Baroness.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
