        <q>Page 193, line 27, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0647P0-02495'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0647P0_20030410_GCR_158' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="bold">"93AA DUTY TO PROMOTE THE EFFICIENT USE OF WATER</span>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0647P0-02496'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0647P0_20030410_GCR_159' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (1) It shall be the duty of every water undertaker to promote the efficient use of water by its customers.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0647P0-02497'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0647P0_20030410_GCR_160' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
