          <p class='first-para'>
            I support what the Minister has just said. There have been a number of cases in which it was obvious that the fines have not been
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_104gc' title='Col. 104GC &mdash; HL Deb 10 April 2003 vol 647 c104GC' name='column_104gc' href='#column_104gc' rel='bookmark'>104GC</a>
            adequate and the public have reacted with dismay because the regulations were not effective enough in this regard. His comments were very important indeed.
