        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_105gc' title='Col. 105GC &mdash; HL Deb 10 April 2003 vol 647 c105GC' name='column_105gc' href='#column_105gc' rel='bookmark'>105GC</a>
        a trust for that purpose. Other water companies with which I am less familiar may do the same. However, some companies still do not allow access and some allow very restricted access&#x2014;just for fishing, for example, but for no other purposes.
